   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Active alarms can be seen in the alarm stack. To enter the
alarm stack:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Star/number 0 key</b>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Use the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Arrow keys</b> to move up and down in the alarm
stack. The alarm stack ends with the text <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">No (further) alarm</codeph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">To leave the alarm stack press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Back key</b> or wait
30 seconds.</p>
               </li>
            </ol>
         </p>
